{"tid":277783,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[中史撚] 有無人覺得3000年歷史 最好J都係三國時代？","createTime":"2017-06-10T02:18:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-13T04:18:06.000Z","uid":52658,"like":8,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"08032099c88ff4e004c478e48618f5a73318a7ed","tid":277783,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T02:18:16.000Z","msg":"26年之內 由州牧割據 無數個諸侯發展到淨低三個國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n再打左60年 點知最後三國都輸左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n96年間出左無數咁多個名臣猛將<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有無人一樣好"},{"pid":"dc414feb18f74f7e3547938694ae60a7c3ac130d","tid":277783,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T02:20:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">36年</span>之內 由州牧割據 無數個諸侯發展到淨低三個國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n再打左60年 點知最後三國都輸左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n96年間出左無數咁多個名臣猛將<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有無人一樣好</blockquote>"},{"pid":"ad82779afa0a52b104bded8709034b7e8cf4e6be","tid":277783,"uid":52658,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T02:27:34.000Z","msg":"好中意三國時代既成語故事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時同人whatsapp都會用下 拋下書包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n望梅止渴<br />\n妄自菲薄<br />\n龍盤虎據<br />\n樂不思蜀<br />\n如魚得水<br />\n吳下阿蒙<br />\n才高八斗<br />\n得隴望蜀etc<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n隨口都up到幾個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20fcdcb2d28d9688017041cee20f335c726153da","tid":277783,"uid":20531,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T02:29:39.000Z","msg":"最好j既係春秋戰國，百家爭鳴"},{"pid":"2d363e425900b11c3e02dac33843db876fd214ca","tid":277783,"uid":3296,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T02:36:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最好j既係春秋戰國，百家爭鳴</blockquote><br />\n最諗唔明一樣野<br />\n點解得三國無雙冇春秋戰國無雙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7939c03629cc970df7d2175111d8182c15214f3","tid":277783,"uid":87511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T02:38:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>最好j既係春秋戰國，百家爭鳴</blockquote><br />\n最諗唔明一樣野<br />\n點解得三國無雙冇春秋戰國無雙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n戰國勉強OK<br />\n計埋春秋時間會好長"},{"pid":"77a92966a6d02a22b69036c14d1ba4c75c5c59b9","tid":277783,"uid":52658,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T02:40:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>最好j既係春秋戰國，百家爭鳴</blockquote><br />\n最諗唔明一樣野<br />\n點解得三國無雙冇春秋戰國無雙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我反而第二中意係秦末至漢初呢八年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 史稱楚漢相爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54013c66c9f1c3ed289eba4a1554a19aee4f19d9","tid":277783,"uid":294,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T02:48:54.000Z","msg":"韓信 項羽屌打三國班友la"},{"pid":"4d37fae90a41378aca6bf0ed8e2888cd3803123d","tid":277783,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T02:55:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>韓信 項羽屌打三國班友la</blockquote><br />\n但楚漢最出名黎黎去去都係得果幾個<br />\n楚就項羽范增英布彭越章邯<br />\n漢就韓信陳平蕭何張良樊噲曹參夏侯嬰周勃<br />\n<br />\n但三國最出名果班 就算唔識歷史既閒閒地都數得出廿幾三十個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce0cdcc34bada22043bb332ba69da86a34d184d7","tid":277783,"uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T03:18:41.000Z","msg":"春秋戰國撚揮手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44c2a5037424c8678caeab9fe5b8803100b8e9f6","tid":277783,"u